    "title": "אֱֽלֹהִים בָּאוּ גוֹיִם | Elohim Baü Goyim — a qinah on Tishah b'Av for 7 October by Isaac Gantwerk Mayer",
    "author": "Isaac Gantwerk Mayer",
    "coauthors": [
        {
            "name": "Isaac Gantwerk Mayer",
            "bio": "From a family of musicians, Isaac Gantwerk Mayer believes that creative art is one of the most powerful ways to get in touch with the divine. He composes music and poetry in Hebrew and English. (He also <a href=\"/index.php?user_ID=342\">translates</a> and <a href=\"/index.php?user_ID=820\">transcribes</a> Hebrew and Aramaic texts, adding <em>niqqud</em> and <em>t'amim</em> as needed.) Isaac runs a Jewish music transcription service, which will transcribe and set any Jewish music in any language, recorded or written. Contact his service on <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/pg/isaacgmayerjewishtranscription/\">Facebook</a> or via <a href=\"https://igmjewishcreativeworks.com/contact\">his music blog</a>.",
            "website": "https://igmjewishcreativeworks.com",
            "avatar": "https://opensiddur.org/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/isaac-gantwerk-mayer-2021-e1674561264977-96x96.jpg",
            "profile_link": "https://opensiddur.org/profile/isaac-gantwerk-mayer"
        }
    ],
    "date": "2025-07-27",
    "last_updated": "2025-08-29",
    "excerpt": "A qinah for 7 October and the hostages, to be recited as part of the Tishah b'Av liturgy.  . . .",
    "content": "<div class=\"english\" lang=\"eng-Latn\" style=\"font-size: 1.2em;\">\nA qinah for 7 October and the hostages, to be recited as part of the Tishah b&#8217;Av liturgy.</p>\n<p>Note: “<span class=\"divine-referent\">The CAUSE</span>” is used to translate the Divine Name <span class=\"divine-referent\">YHVH</span>, based on the philosophical idea of <span class=\"divine-referent\">God</span> as the <span class=\"divine-referent\">Prime Mover</span> and on the interpretation of <span class=\"divine-referent\">the Name</span> as a causative form of the copula – “causes to be.” “<span class=\"divine-referent\">God</span>” is used to translate the divine name <span class=\"divine-referent\">Elohim</span>. All divine referents (pronouns, epithets, names) are rendered in <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Unicase\">unicase</a>.\n</div>\n<hr />\n<table style=\"margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" class=\"draggable toggleable-table\">\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th id=\"x\" style=\"text-align: right;\">Source (Hebrew)</th>\n<th style=\"text-align: left;\">Translation (English)</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top;\">\n<div class=\"liturgy\" lang=\"heb-Hebr\" style=\"text-align: right;\">\nאֱֽלֹהִ֡ים בָּ֤אוּ גוֹיִ֨ם ׀ בְּֽנַחֲלָתֶ֗ךָ <span class=\"citation\">(תהלים עט:א)</span><br />\n<span class=\"acrostic\">אֳ</span>פָקִים נִתְּנוּ לְטִבְחַת גְּבוּלוֹתֶֽיךָ<br />\n<span class=\"acrostic\">בְּ</span>אֵרִי מֻצְּתָה מִמֵּימֶֽיהָ מֻפְשָׁט מוֹשָׁבִי׃<br />\nבְּתוּלֹתַ֥י וּבַחוּרַ֖י הָלְכ֥וּ בַשֶּֽׁבִי׃ <span class=\"citation\">(איכה א:יח)</span>\n</div>\n</td>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top;\">\n<div class=\"english\" lang=\"eng-Latn\" style=\"text-align: left;\">\n<span class=\"divine-referent\">God</span>, nations entered Your inheritance! <span class=\"citation\">(Psalms 79:1)</span><br />\nHorizons<span class=\"footnote_referrer\"><a role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\" onclick=\"footnote_moveToReference__1('footnote_plugin_reference__1_1');\" onkeypress=\"footnote_moveToReference__1('footnote_plugin_reference__1_1');\" ><sup id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip__1_1\" class=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text\">[1]</sup></a><span id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text__1_1\" class=\"footnote_tooltip\"> Hebrew: <em>Ofakim</em>. The name of one of the towns attacked on 7 October.&nbsp;</span></span><script type=\"text/javascript\"> jQuery('#footnote_plugin_tooltip__1_1').tooltip({ tip: '#footnote_plugin_tooltip_text__1_1', tipClass: 'footnote_tooltip', effect: 'fade', predelay: 0, fadeInSpeed: 200, delay: 400, fadeOutSpeed: 200, position: 'center right', relative: true, offset: [0, 0], });</script> were given to Your borders’ slaughter. <span class=\"acrostic\">&nbsp;</span><br />\nMy well<span class=\"footnote_referrer\"><a role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\" onclick=\"footnote_moveToReference__1('footnote_plugin_reference__1_2');\" onkeypress=\"footnote_moveToReference__1('footnote_plugin_reference__1_2');\" ><sup id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip__1_2\" class=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text\">[2]</sup></a><span id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text__1_2\" class=\"footnote_tooltip\"> Hebrew: <em>B’eri</em>. The name of one of the towns attacked on 7 October.&nbsp;</span></span><script type=\"text/javascript\"> jQuery('#footnote_plugin_tooltip__1_2').tooltip({ tip: '#footnote_plugin_tooltip_text__1_2', tipClass: 'footnote_tooltip', effect: 'fade', predelay: 0, fadeInSpeed: 200, delay: 400, fadeOutSpeed: 200, position: 'center right', relative: true, offset: [0, 0], });</script> was drained of her waters, my town was stripped <span class=\"acrostic\">&nbsp;</span><br />\n— my young women and men taken captive! <span class=\"citation\">(Lamentations 1:18)</span>\n</div>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top;\">\n<div class=\"liturgy\" lang=\"heb-Hebr\" style=\"text-align: right;\">\nנָתְנ֡וּ אֶת־נִבְלַ֬ת עֲבָדֶ֗יךָ מַ֭אֲכָל <span class=\"citation\">(תהלים עט:ב)</span><br />\n<span class=\"acrostic\">גִּ</span>בְעוֹת הַנֶּגֶב נִשְׂרְפוּ כַּהֵיכָל<br />\n<span class=\"acrostic\">דָּ</span>ם נִשְׁפַּךְ וּלְנַקּוֹתוֹ מִי יוּכַל<br />\n<span class=\"acrostic\">הָ</span>עֲשָׂרָה בִּנְתִיבוֹתֵיהֶם כׇּל־אֶחָד שָׁכַל<br />\n<span class=\"acrostic\">וּ</span>מִשָּׁמַֽיִם זָעַק אֲהָהּ אֵל הִסְתַּכַּל<br />\n<span class=\"acrostic\">זִ</span>קְנֵי עַמְּךָ כּוֹאֲבִים אֶת־מַכְאוֹבִי׃<br />\nבְּתוּלֹתַ֥י וּבַחוּרַ֖י הָלְכ֥וּ בַשֶּֽׁבִי׃ <span class=\"citation\">(איכה א:יח)</span>\n</div>\n</td>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top;\">\n<div class=\"english\" lang=\"eng-Latn\" style=\"text-align: left;\">\nThey gave the corpses of Your servants as carrion! <span class=\"citation\">(Psalms 79:2)</span><br />\nThe hills of the southland were burned like the Temple. <span class=\"acrostic\">&nbsp;</span><br />\nBlood was spilt, and who can clean it? <span class=\"acrostic\">&nbsp;</span><br />\nThe ten, in their paths,<span class=\"footnote_referrer\"><a role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\" onclick=\"footnote_moveToReference__1('footnote_plugin_reference__1_3');\" onkeypress=\"footnote_moveToReference__1('footnote_plugin_reference__1_3');\" ><sup id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip__1_3\" class=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text\">[3]</sup></a><span id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text__1_3\" class=\"footnote_tooltip\"> A twofold reference. Referring to Netiv haAsarah (lit: Path of the Ten), one of the towns attacked on 7 October. Also referring to the ten martyrs whose deaths at the hand of the Romans are referenced in the Tishah b’Av and Yom Kippur liturgies.&nbsp;</span></span><script type=\"text/javascript\"> jQuery('#footnote_plugin_tooltip__1_3').tooltip({ tip: '#footnote_plugin_tooltip_text__1_3', tipClass: 'footnote_tooltip', effect: 'fade', predelay: 0, fadeInSpeed: 200, delay: 400, fadeOutSpeed: 200, position: 'center right', relative: true, offset: [0, 0], });</script> each one was bereaved, <span class=\"acrostic\">&nbsp;</span><br />\nand from heaven cried: “Alas! O <span class=\"divine-referent\">Deity</span>, look! <span class=\"acrostic\">&nbsp;</span><br />\nYour people’s elders are suffering my suffering!” <span class=\"acrostic\">&nbsp;</span><br />\n— my young women and men taken captive! <span class=\"citation\">(Lamentations 1:18)</span>\n</div>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top;\">\n<div class=\"liturgy\" lang=\"heb-Hebr\" style=\"text-align: right;\">\nשָׁפְכ֬וּ דָמָ֨ם ׀ כַּמַּ֗יִם <span class=\"citation\">(תהלים עט:ג)</span><br />\n<span class=\"acrostic\">ח</span>וֹלִית כְּמוֹ־חוֹל בְּעֵינַֽיִם<br />\n<span class=\"acrostic\">טָ</span>בְעוּ שְׁעָרֶיהָ כִּפְלַֽיִם<br />\n<span class=\"acrostic\">יָ</span>כִינִי נִהְיְתָה כִּירוּשָׁלַֽיִם<br />\n<span class=\"acrostic\">כָּ</span>לְאוּ אֶת־יוֹנְקֵי שָׁדַֽיִם<br />\n<span class=\"acrostic\">לְ</span>חׇרְבָּה מִי־יִבְנֶה פַּעֲמַֽיִם<br />\n<span class=\"acrostic\">מִ</span>י־יָשׁוּב בְּקוֹל שֽׁוּבִי שֽׁוּבִי׃<br />\nבְּתוּלֹתַ֥י וּבַחוּרַ֖י הָלְכ֥וּ בַשֶּֽׁבִי׃ <span class=\"citation\">(איכה א:יח)</span>\n</div>\n</td>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top;\">\n<div class=\"english\" lang=\"eng-Latn\" style=\"text-align: left;\">\nThey spilt blood like water! <span class=\"citation\">(Psalms 79:3)</span><br />\nḤolit,<span class=\"footnote_referrer\"><a role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\" onclick=\"footnote_moveToReference__1('footnote_plugin_reference__1_4');\" onkeypress=\"footnote_moveToReference__1('footnote_plugin_reference__1_4');\" ><sup id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip__1_4\" class=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text\">[4]</sup></a><span id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text__1_4\" class=\"footnote_tooltip\"> One of the towns attacked on 7 October. Literally: “sand dune”&nbsp;</span></span><script type=\"text/javascript\"> jQuery('#footnote_plugin_tooltip__1_4').tooltip({ tip: '#footnote_plugin_tooltip_text__1_4', tipClass: 'footnote_tooltip', effect: 'fade', predelay: 0, fadeInSpeed: 200, delay: 400, fadeOutSpeed: 200, position: 'center right', relative: true, offset: [0, 0], });</script> like sand in the eyes.<span class=\"footnote_referrer\"><a role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\" onclick=\"footnote_moveToReference__1('footnote_plugin_reference__1_5');\" onkeypress=\"footnote_moveToReference__1('footnote_plugin_reference__1_5');\" ><sup id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip__1_5\" class=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text\">[5]</sup></a><span id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text__1_5\" class=\"footnote_tooltip\"> i.e. it brings one to tears&nbsp;</span></span><script type=\"text/javascript\"> jQuery('#footnote_plugin_tooltip__1_5').tooltip({ tip: '#footnote_plugin_tooltip_text__1_5', tipClass: 'footnote_tooltip', effect: 'fade', predelay: 0, fadeInSpeed: 200, delay: 400, fadeOutSpeed: 200, position: 'center right', relative: true, offset: [0, 0], });</script> <span class=\"acrostic\">&nbsp;</span><br />\nHer gates sunk<span class=\"footnote_referrer\"><a role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\" onclick=\"footnote_moveToReference__1('footnote_plugin_reference__1_6');\" onkeypress=\"footnote_moveToReference__1('footnote_plugin_reference__1_6');\" ><sup id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip__1_6\" class=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text\">[6]</sup></a><span id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text__1_6\" class=\"footnote_tooltip\"> A twofold reference. Referring to Sha’ar haNegev (lit: Gate of the Negev), the regional council most severely impacted by the attacks on 7 October. Also a reference to Lamentations 2:9&nbsp;</span></span><script type=\"text/javascript\"> jQuery('#footnote_plugin_tooltip__1_6').tooltip({ tip: '#footnote_plugin_tooltip_text__1_6', tipClass: 'footnote_tooltip', effect: 'fade', predelay: 0, fadeInSpeed: 200, delay: 400, fadeOutSpeed: 200, position: 'center right', relative: true, offset: [0, 0], });</script> doubly. <span class=\"acrostic\">&nbsp;</span><br />\nYakhini<span class=\"footnote_referrer\"><a role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\" onclick=\"footnote_moveToReference__1('footnote_plugin_reference__1_7');\" onkeypress=\"footnote_moveToReference__1('footnote_plugin_reference__1_7');\" ><sup id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip__1_7\" class=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text\">[7]</sup></a><span id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text__1_7\" class=\"footnote_tooltip\"> One of the towns attacked on 7 October.&nbsp;</span></span><script type=\"text/javascript\"> jQuery('#footnote_plugin_tooltip__1_7').tooltip({ tip: '#footnote_plugin_tooltip_text__1_7', tipClass: 'footnote_tooltip', effect: 'fade', predelay: 0, fadeInSpeed: 200, delay: 400, fadeOutSpeed: 200, position: 'center right', relative: true, offset: [0, 0], });</script> became like Jerusalem. <span class=\"acrostic\">&nbsp;</span><br />\nThey imprisoned suckling babies! <span class=\"acrostic\">&nbsp;</span><br />\nTo destruction, who will build a second time? <span class=\"acrostic\">&nbsp;</span><br />\nWho will return at the sound of “Return, return?”<span class=\"footnote_referrer\"><a role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\" onclick=\"footnote_moveToReference__1('footnote_plugin_reference__1_8');\" onkeypress=\"footnote_moveToReference__1('footnote_plugin_reference__1_8');\" ><sup id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip__1_8\" class=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text\">[8]</sup></a><span id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text__1_8\" class=\"footnote_tooltip\"> A reference to Song of Songs 7:1&nbsp;</span></span><script type=\"text/javascript\"> jQuery('#footnote_plugin_tooltip__1_8').tooltip({ tip: '#footnote_plugin_tooltip_text__1_8', tipClass: 'footnote_tooltip', effect: 'fade', predelay: 0, fadeInSpeed: 200, delay: 400, fadeOutSpeed: 200, position: 'center right', relative: true, offset: [0, 0], });</script> <span class=\"acrostic\">&nbsp;</span><br />\n— my young women and men taken captive! <span class=\"citation\">(Lamentations 1:18)</span>\n</div>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top;\">\n<div class=\"liturgy\" lang=\"heb-Hebr\" style=\"text-align: right;\">\nהָיִ֣ינוּ חֶ֭רְפָּה לִשְׁכֵנֵ֑ינוּ <span class=\"citation\">(תהלים עט:ד)</span><br />\n<span class=\"acrostic\">נ</span>וֹבָה הֻשְׁתַּק נִגּוּנֵֽינוּ<br />\n<span class=\"acrostic\">סֻ</span>גְּפוּ אֹהֲבֵי פִּזְמוֹנֵֽנוּ<br />\n<span class=\"acrostic\">עַ</span>זָּה כַּמָּֽוֶת חֶדְלוֹן לְחָנֵֽינוּ<br />\n<span class=\"acrostic\">פְּ</span>סַנְתֵּרִין וְסוּמְפֹּנְיָה בַּל־יְשַׂמְּחוּ אֶת־לִבִּי׃<br />\nבְּתוּלֹתַ֥י וּבַחוּרַ֖י הָלְכ֥וּ בַשֶּֽׁבִי׃ <span class=\"citation\">(איכה א:יח)</span>\n</div>\n</td>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top;\">\n<div class=\"english\" lang=\"eng-Latn\" style=\"text-align: left;\">\nWe have become the reproach of our neighbors! <span class=\"citation\">(Psalms 79:4)</span><br />\nNova<span class=\"footnote_referrer\"><a role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\" onclick=\"footnote_moveToReference__1('footnote_plugin_reference__1_9');\" onkeypress=\"footnote_moveToReference__1('footnote_plugin_reference__1_9');\" ><sup id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip__1_9\" class=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text\">[9]</sup></a><span id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text__1_9\" class=\"footnote_tooltip\"> One of the music festivals attacked on 7 October.&nbsp;</span></span><script type=\"text/javascript\"> jQuery('#footnote_plugin_tooltip__1_9').tooltip({ tip: '#footnote_plugin_tooltip_text__1_9', tipClass: 'footnote_tooltip', effect: 'fade', predelay: 0, fadeInSpeed: 200, delay: 400, fadeOutSpeed: 200, position: 'center right', relative: true, offset: [0, 0], });</script> — our melody was silenced. <span class=\"acrostic\">&nbsp;</span><br />\nThe lovers of our choruses were tormented. <span class=\"acrostic\">&nbsp;</span><br />\nStrong as death<span class=\"footnote_referrer\"><a role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\" onclick=\"footnote_moveToReference__1('footnote_plugin_reference__1_10');\" onkeypress=\"footnote_moveToReference__1('footnote_plugin_reference__1_10');\" ><sup id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip__1_10\" class=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text\">[10]</sup></a><span id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text__1_10\" class=\"footnote_tooltip\"> A twofold reference. The word “strong” in Hebrew is ‘azza, a homonym of Gaza. Also a reference to Song of Songs 8:6&nbsp;</span></span><script type=\"text/javascript\"> jQuery('#footnote_plugin_tooltip__1_10').tooltip({ tip: '#footnote_plugin_tooltip_text__1_10', tipClass: 'footnote_tooltip', effect: 'fade', predelay: 0, fadeInSpeed: 200, delay: 400, fadeOutSpeed: 200, position: 'center right', relative: true, offset: [0, 0], });</script> is the ceasing of our tunes. <span class=\"acrostic\">&nbsp;</span><br />\nPsaltery and symphony,<span class=\"footnote_referrer\"><a role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\" onclick=\"footnote_moveToReference__1('footnote_plugin_reference__1_11');\" onkeypress=\"footnote_moveToReference__1('footnote_plugin_reference__1_11');\" ><sup id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip__1_11\" class=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text\">[11]</sup></a><span id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text__1_11\" class=\"footnote_tooltip\"> Find Daniel 3:15&nbsp;</span></span><script type=\"text/javascript\"> jQuery('#footnote_plugin_tooltip__1_11').tooltip({ tip: '#footnote_plugin_tooltip_text__1_11', tipClass: 'footnote_tooltip', effect: 'fade', predelay: 0, fadeInSpeed: 200, delay: 400, fadeOutSpeed: 200, position: 'center right', relative: true, offset: [0, 0], });</script> let them not cheer up my heart! <span class=\"acrostic\">&nbsp;</span><br />\n— my young women and men taken captive! <span class=\"citation\">(Lamentations 1:18)</span>\n</div>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top;\">\n<div class=\"liturgy\" lang=\"heb-Hebr\" style=\"text-align: right;\">\nעַד־מָ֣ה יְ֭הֹוָה תֶּאֱנַ֣ף לָנֶ֑צַח <span class=\"citation\">(תהלים עט:ה)</span><br />\n<span class=\"acrostic\">צַ</span>דֵּק דִּין בְּנֵי פְּסַיידָּאק הַנְּתוּנִים לְרֶֽצַח<br />\n<span class=\"acrostic\">קָ</span>רַֽעְנוּ בְּגָדֵֽינוּ עַל־מְפִיצֵי קֶֽצַח<br />\n<span class=\"acrostic\">רְ</span>עַם אֵל עֶלְיוֹן דְּרֹךְ פּוּרָם הַזֵּה נֵֽצַח<br />\n<span class=\"acrostic\">שְׂ</span>דֵרוֹתֵינוּ תְּחֻסַּֽנָּה בַּת־עַמִּי תּוּשְׁבִי׃<br />\nבְּנֵ֣י הַמְּדִינָ֗ה הָֽעֹלִים֙ מִשֶּׁבִ֣י׃\n</div>\n</td>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top;\">\n<div class=\"english\" lang=\"eng-Latn\" style=\"text-align: left;\">\nUntil what, <span class=\"divine-referent\">Cause</span>, will You rage eternal? <span class=\"citation\">(Psalms 79:5)</span><br />\nJustify the judgment of those of Psyduck,<span class=\"footnote_referrer\"><a role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\" onclick=\"footnote_moveToReference__1('footnote_plugin_reference__1_12');\" onkeypress=\"footnote_moveToReference__1('footnote_plugin_reference__1_12');\" ><sup id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip__1_12\" class=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text\">[12]</sup></a><span id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text__1_12\" class=\"footnote_tooltip\"> One of the music festivals attacked on 7 October.&nbsp;</span></span><script type=\"text/javascript\"> jQuery('#footnote_plugin_tooltip__1_12').tooltip({ tip: '#footnote_plugin_tooltip_text__1_12', tipClass: 'footnote_tooltip', effect: 'fade', predelay: 0, fadeInSpeed: 200, delay: 400, fadeOutSpeed: 200, position: 'center right', relative: true, offset: [0, 0], });</script> given over to murder. <span class=\"acrostic\">&nbsp;</span><br />\nWe have torn our clothes for those scattering nigella.<span class=\"footnote_referrer\"><a role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\" onclick=\"footnote_moveToReference__1('footnote_plugin_reference__1_13');\" onkeypress=\"footnote_moveToReference__1('footnote_plugin_reference__1_13');\" ><sup id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip__1_13\" class=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text\">[13]</sup></a><span id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text__1_13\" class=\"footnote_tooltip\"> Find Isaiah 28:25&nbsp;</span></span><script type=\"text/javascript\"> jQuery('#footnote_plugin_tooltip__1_13').tooltip({ tip: '#footnote_plugin_tooltip_text__1_13', tipClass: 'footnote_tooltip', effect: 'fade', predelay: 0, fadeInSpeed: 200, delay: 400, fadeOutSpeed: 200, position: 'center right', relative: true, offset: [0, 0], });</script> <span class=\"acrostic\">&nbsp;</span><br />\nThunder, <span class=\"divine-referent\">Highest Deity</span>! Tread their vintage! Splatter their juice!<span class=\"footnote_referrer\"><a role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\" onclick=\"footnote_moveToReference__1('footnote_plugin_reference__1_14');\" onkeypress=\"footnote_moveToReference__1('footnote_plugin_reference__1_14');\" ><sup id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip__1_14\" class=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text\">[14]</sup></a><span id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text__1_14\" class=\"footnote_tooltip\"> Find Isaiah 63:3&nbsp;</span></span><script type=\"text/javascript\"> jQuery('#footnote_plugin_tooltip__1_14').tooltip({ tip: '#footnote_plugin_tooltip_text__1_14', tipClass: 'footnote_tooltip', effect: 'fade', predelay: 0, fadeInSpeed: 200, delay: 400, fadeOutSpeed: 200, position: 'center right', relative: true, offset: [0, 0], });</script> <span class=\"acrostic\">&nbsp;</span><br />\nOur avenues<span class=\"footnote_referrer\"><a role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\" onclick=\"footnote_moveToReference__1('footnote_plugin_reference__1_15');\" onkeypress=\"footnote_moveToReference__1('footnote_plugin_reference__1_15');\" ><sup id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip__1_15\" class=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text\">[15]</sup></a><span id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text__1_15\" class=\"footnote_tooltip\"> Hebrew: <em>sderotenu</em>. A reference to Sderot, one of the cities attacked on 7 October.&nbsp;</span></span><script type=\"text/javascript\"> jQuery('#footnote_plugin_tooltip__1_15').tooltip({ tip: '#footnote_plugin_tooltip_text__1_15', tipClass: 'footnote_tooltip', effect: 'fade', predelay: 0, fadeInSpeed: 200, delay: 400, fadeOutSpeed: 200, position: 'center right', relative: true, offset: [0, 0], });</script> will be strengthened; you will be returned, my poor people! <span class=\"acrostic\">&nbsp;</span><br />\nThe children of the land who ascend up from captivity!<span class=\"footnote_referrer\"><a role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\" onclick=\"footnote_moveToReference__1('footnote_plugin_reference__1_16');\" onkeypress=\"footnote_moveToReference__1('footnote_plugin_reference__1_16');\" ><sup id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip__1_16\" class=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text\">[16]</sup></a><span id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text__1_16\" class=\"footnote_tooltip\"> Ezra 2:1, adjusted with pausal form&nbsp;</span></span><script type=\"text/javascript\"> jQuery('#footnote_plugin_tooltip__1_16').tooltip({ tip: '#footnote_plugin_tooltip_text__1_16', tipClass: 'footnote_tooltip', effect: 'fade', predelay: 0, fadeInSpeed: 200, delay: 400, fadeOutSpeed: 200, position: 'center right', relative: true, offset: [0, 0], });</script>\n</div>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top;\">\n<div class=\"liturgy\" lang=\"heb-Hebr\" style=\"text-align: right;\">\n<span class=\"acrostic\">תָּ֤</span>ב֣וֹא לְפָנֶיךָ֮ אֶנְקַ֢ת אָ֫סִ֥יר<br />\nכְּגֹ֥דֶל זְרוֹעֲךָ֑ ה֝וֹתֵ֗ר בְּנֵ֣י תְמוּתָֽה׃<br />\nוְהָ֘שֵׁ֤ב לִשְׁכֵנֵ֣ינוּ שִׁ֭בְעָתַיִם<br />\nאֶל־חֵיקָ֑ם חֶרְפָּ֘תָ֤ם<br />\nאֲשֶׁ֖ר חֵרְפ֣וּךָ אֲדֹנָֽי׃<br />\nוַאֲנַ֤חְנוּ עַמְּךָ֨ ׀<br />\nוְצֹ֥אן מַרְעִיתֶךָ֮<br />\nנ֤וֹדֶ֥ה לְּךָ֗ לְע֫וֹלָ֥ם<br />\nלְד֥וֹר וָדֹ֑ר<br />\nנְ֝סַפֵּ֗ר תְּהִלָּתֶֽךָ׃ <span class=\"citation\">(תהלים עט:יא-יג)</span>\n</div>\n</td>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top;\">\n<div class=\"english\" lang=\"eng-Latn\" style=\"text-align: left;\">\nLet the prisoners’ groans come before You;<br />\nby Your great arm free those condemned to death.<br />\nAnd return upon our neighbors sevenfold<br />\nupon their laps the shame<br />\nby which they shamed You, <span class=\"divine-referent\">Master</span>.<br />\nAnd we are Your people<br />\nand the flock You shepherd;<br />\nwe thank You forever,<br />\nfrom generation to generation<br />\nwe tell Your praises.<span class=\"footnote_referrer\"><a role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\" onclick=\"footnote_moveToReference__1('footnote_plugin_reference__1_17');\" onkeypress=\"footnote_moveToReference__1('footnote_plugin_reference__1_17');\" ><sup id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip__1_17\" class=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text\">[17]</sup></a><span id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text__1_17\" class=\"footnote_tooltip\"> These verses serving as a doxology concluding the lament&nbsp;</span></span><script type=\"text/javascript\"> jQuery('#footnote_plugin_tooltip__1_17').tooltip({ tip: '#footnote_plugin_tooltip_text__1_17', tipClass: 'footnote_tooltip', effect: 'fade', predelay: 0, fadeInSpeed: 200, delay: 400, fadeOutSpeed: 200, position: 'center right', relative: true, offset: [0, 0], });</script> <span class=\"citation\">(Psalm 79:11-13)</span>\n</div>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<div class=\"speaker-mute footnotes_reference_container\"> <div class=\"footnote_container_prepare\"><p><span role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\" class=\"footnote_reference_container_label pointer\" onclick=\"footnote_expand_collapse_reference_container__1();\">Notes</span><span role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\" class=\"footnote_reference_container_collapse_button\" style=\"display: none;; display: none;\" onclick=\"footnote_expand_collapse_reference_container__1();\"></span></p></div> <div id=\"footnote_references_container__1\" style=\"\"><table class=\"footnotes_table footnote-reference-container\"><caption class=\"accessibility\">Notes</caption> <tbody> \r\n\r\n<tr class=\"footnotes_plugin_reference_row\"> <th scope=\"row\" id=\"footnote_plugin_reference__1_1\" class=\"footnote_plugin_index pointer\" onclick=\"footnote_moveToAnchor__1('footnote_plugin_tooltip__1_1');\"><a role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\" class=\"footnote_plugin_link\" >1</a></th> <td class=\"footnote_plugin_text\">Hebrew: <em>Ofakim</em>. The name of one of the towns attacked on 7 October.</td></tr>\r\n\r\n<tr class=\"footnotes_plugin_reference_row\"> <th scope=\"row\" id=\"footnote_plugin_reference__1_2\" class=\"footnote_plugin_index pointer\" onclick=\"footnote_moveToAnchor__1('footnote_plugin_tooltip__1_2');\"><a role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\" class=\"footnote_plugin_link\" >2</a></th> <td class=\"footnote_plugin_text\">Hebrew: <em>B’eri</em>. The name of one of the towns attacked on 7 October.</td></tr>\r\n\r\n<tr class=\"footnotes_plugin_reference_row\"> <th scope=\"row\" id=\"footnote_plugin_reference__1_3\" class=\"footnote_plugin_index pointer\" onclick=\"footnote_moveToAnchor__1('footnote_plugin_tooltip__1_3');\"><a role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\" class=\"footnote_plugin_link\" >3</a></th> <td class=\"footnote_plugin_text\">A twofold reference. Referring to Netiv haAsarah (lit: Path of the Ten), one of the towns attacked on 7 October. Also referring to the ten martyrs whose deaths at the hand of the Romans are referenced in the Tishah b’Av and Yom Kippur liturgies.</td></tr>\r\n\r\n<tr class=\"footnotes_plugin_reference_row\"> <th scope=\"row\" id=\"footnote_plugin_reference__1_4\" class=\"footnote_plugin_index pointer\" onclick=\"footnote_moveToAnchor__1('footnote_plugin_tooltip__1_4');\"><a role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\" class=\"footnote_plugin_link\" >4</a></th> <td class=\"footnote_plugin_text\">One of the towns attacked on 7 October. Literally: “sand dune”</td></tr>\r\n\r\n<tr class=\"footnotes_plugin_reference_row\"> <th scope=\"row\" id=\"footnote_plugin_reference__1_5\" class=\"footnote_plugin_index pointer\" onclick=\"footnote_moveToAnchor__1('footnote_plugin_tooltip__1_5');\"><a role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\" class=\"footnote_plugin_link\" >5</a></th> <td class=\"footnote_plugin_text\">i.e. it brings one to tears</td></tr>\r\n\r\n<tr class=\"footnotes_plugin_reference_row\"> <th scope=\"row\" id=\"footnote_plugin_reference__1_6\" class=\"footnote_plugin_index pointer\" onclick=\"footnote_moveToAnchor__1('footnote_plugin_tooltip__1_6');\"><a role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\" class=\"footnote_plugin_link\" >6</a></th> <td class=\"footnote_plugin_text\">A twofold reference. Referring to Sha’ar haNegev (lit: Gate of the Negev), the regional council most severely impacted by the attacks on 7 October. Also a reference to Lamentations 2:9</td></tr>\r\n\r\n<tr class=\"footnotes_plugin_reference_row\"> <th scope=\"row\" id=\"footnote_plugin_reference__1_7\" class=\"footnote_plugin_index pointer\" onclick=\"footnote_moveToAnchor__1('footnote_plugin_tooltip__1_7');\"><a role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\" class=\"footnote_plugin_link\" >7</a></th> <td class=\"footnote_plugin_text\">One of the towns attacked on 7 October.</td></tr>\r\n\r\n<tr class=\"footnotes_plugin_reference_row\"> <th scope=\"row\" id=\"footnote_plugin_reference__1_8\" class=\"footnote_plugin_index pointer\" onclick=\"footnote_moveToAnchor__1('footnote_plugin_tooltip__1_8');\"><a role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\" class=\"footnote_plugin_link\" >8</a></th> <td class=\"footnote_plugin_text\">A reference to Song of Songs 7:1</td></tr>\r\n\r\n<tr class=\"footnotes_plugin_reference_row\"> <th scope=\"row\" id=\"footnote_plugin_reference__1_9\" class=\"footnote_plugin_index pointer\" onclick=\"footnote_moveToAnchor__1('footnote_plugin_tooltip__1_9');\"><a role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\" class=\"footnote_plugin_link\" >9</a></th> <td class=\"footnote_plugin_text\">One of the music festivals attacked on 7 October.</td></tr>\r\n\r\n<tr class=\"footnotes_plugin_reference_row\"> <th scope=\"row\" id=\"footnote_plugin_reference__1_10\" class=\"footnote_plugin_index pointer\" onclick=\"footnote_moveToAnchor__1('footnote_plugin_tooltip__1_10');\"><a role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\" class=\"footnote_plugin_link\" >10</a></th> <td class=\"footnote_plugin_text\">A twofold reference. The word “strong” in Hebrew is ‘azza, a homonym of Gaza. Also a reference to Song of Songs 8:6</td></tr>\r\n\r\n<tr class=\"footnotes_plugin_reference_row\"> <th scope=\"row\" id=\"footnote_plugin_reference__1_11\" class=\"footnote_plugin_index pointer\" onclick=\"footnote_moveToAnchor__1('footnote_plugin_tooltip__1_11');\"><a role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\" class=\"footnote_plugin_link\" >11</a></th> <td class=\"footnote_plugin_text\">Find Daniel 3:15</td></tr>\r\n\r\n<tr class=\"footnotes_plugin_reference_row\"> <th scope=\"row\" id=\"footnote_plugin_reference__1_12\" class=\"footnote_plugin_index pointer\" onclick=\"footnote_moveToAnchor__1('footnote_plugin_tooltip__1_12');\"><a role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\" class=\"footnote_plugin_link\" >12</a></th> <td class=\"footnote_plugin_text\">One of the music festivals attacked on 7 October.</td></tr>\r\n\r\n<tr class=\"footnotes_plugin_reference_row\"> <th scope=\"row\" id=\"footnote_plugin_reference__1_13\" class=\"footnote_plugin_index pointer\" onclick=\"footnote_moveToAnchor__1('footnote_plugin_tooltip__1_13');\"><a role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\" class=\"footnote_plugin_link\" >13</a></th> <td class=\"footnote_plugin_text\">Find Isaiah 28:25</td></tr>\r\n\r\n<tr class=\"footnotes_plugin_reference_row\"> <th scope=\"row\" id=\"footnote_plugin_reference__1_14\" class=\"footnote_plugin_index pointer\" onclick=\"footnote_moveToAnchor__1('footnote_plugin_tooltip__1_14');\"><a role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\" class=\"footnote_plugin_link\" >14</a></th> <td class=\"footnote_plugin_text\">Find Isaiah 63:3</td></tr>\r\n\r\n<tr class=\"footnotes_plugin_reference_row\"> <th scope=\"row\" id=\"footnote_plugin_reference__1_15\" class=\"footnote_plugin_index pointer\" onclick=\"footnote_moveToAnchor__1('footnote_plugin_tooltip__1_15');\"><a role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\" class=\"footnote_plugin_link\" >15</a></th> <td class=\"footnote_plugin_text\">Hebrew: <em>sderotenu</em>. A reference to Sderot, one of the cities attacked on 7 October.</td></tr>\r\n\r\n<tr class=\"footnotes_plugin_reference_row\"> <th scope=\"row\" id=\"footnote_plugin_reference__1_16\" class=\"footnote_plugin_index pointer\" onclick=\"footnote_moveToAnchor__1('footnote_plugin_tooltip__1_16');\"><a role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\" class=\"footnote_plugin_link\" >16</a></th> <td class=\"footnote_plugin_text\">Ezra 2:1, adjusted with pausal form</td></tr>\r\n\r\n<tr class=\"footnotes_plugin_reference_row\"> <th scope=\"row\" id=\"footnote_plugin_reference__1_17\" class=\"footnote_plugin_index pointer\" onclick=\"footnote_moveToAnchor__1('footnote_plugin_tooltip__1_17');\"><a role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\" class=\"footnote_plugin_link\" >17</a></th> <td class=\"footnote_plugin_text\">These verses serving as a doxology concluding the lament</td></tr>\r\n\r\n </tbody> </table> </div></div><script type=\"text/javascript\"> function footnote_expand_reference_container__1() { jQuery('#footnote_references_container__1').show(); jQuery('#footnote_reference_container_collapse_button__1').text('−'); } function footnote_collapse_reference_container__1() { jQuery('#footnote_references_container__1').hide(); jQuery('#footnote_reference_container_collapse_button__1').text('+'); } function footnote_expand_collapse_reference_container__1() { if (jQuery('#footnote_references_container__1').is(':hidden')) { footnote_expand_reference_container__1(); } else { footnote_collapse_reference_container__1(); } } function footnote_moveToReference__1(p_str_TargetID) { footnote_expand_reference_container__1(); var l_obj_Target = jQuery('#' + p_str_TargetID); if (l_obj_Target.length) { jQuery( 'html, body' ).delay( 0 ); jQuery('html, body').animate({ scrollTop: l_obj_Target.offset().top - window.innerHeight * 0.2 }, 380); } } function footnote_moveToAnchor__1(p_str_TargetID) { footnote_expand_reference_container__1(); var l_obj_Target = jQuery('#' + p_str_TargetID); if (l_obj_Target.length) { jQuery( 'html, body' ).delay( 0 ); jQuery('html, body').animate({ scrollTop: l_obj_Target.offset().top - window.innerHeight * 0.2 }, 380); } }</script>",
